{"tid":944110,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[等食血饅頭]內地上月二手樓樓價下跌城市擴大至到17個","createTime":"2018-12-17T02:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T10:29:45.000Z","uid":57424,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"55eb10ba1d03683ca2870872aff72e1ea6516242","tid":944110,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T02:15:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=331006\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D331006&d=t%2F78%2BODoCXm3BL3z0AU5BRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=b82c3e78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D331006&h=cf184150\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=331006</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】內地上月二手樓樓價按月下跌的城市擴大至到17個。<br />\n<br />\n國家統計局前日公布內地70個大中城市的樓價數據，其中二手樓價格按月下跌的城市數量，由10月的14個，擴大至到17個，下跌城市數量是連續3個月增加。<br />\n<br />\n在10月和11月連續2個月有超過10個城市的二手樓價下跌，是近4年來首次出現，其中四大一線城市二手樓樓價跌幅擴大，中原地產首席分析員張大偉認為，從二手樓價看內地樓價轉勢點已經出現。<br />\n<br />\n一線城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"517e0bcaf8e1e81b00fb3e0db3c1d23848b4d685","tid":944110,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T02:32:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「樓價跌城市數量」<br />\n唔知跌幅點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c0f91bb68fb845f937472cda46cbbbe455741c","tid":944110,"uid":57848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:27:50.000Z","msg":"內地樓價跌=熱錢湧入香港=樓市gogogo"},{"pid":"d2dd4d17f7a927e25d0428f52f8ae714fc14023f","tid":944110,"uid":112720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0c0f91bb68fb845f937472cda46cbbbe455741c","tid":944110,"uid":57848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:27:50.000Z","msg":"內地樓價跌=熱錢湧入香港=樓市gogogo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-1